HVY MUr'aH VNG'aLH H'yYUr HYVNH.
L'a ShM'yH BQVL L'a LQChH MVSUr BYHVH L'a BTChH 'aL-'aLHYH L'a QUrBH.
ShUrYH BQUrBH 'aUrYVTh Sh'aGYM ShPhTYH Z'aBY 'yUrB L'a GUrMV LBQUr.
NBY'aYH PhChZYM 'aNShY BGDVTh KHNYH ChLLV-QDSh ChMSV ThVUrH.
YHVH TShDYQ BQUrBH L'a Y'yShH 'yVLH BBQUr BBQUr MShPhTV YThN L'aVUr L'a N'yDUr VL'a-YVD'y 'yVL BShTh.
HKUrThY GVYM NShMV PhNVThM HChUrBThY ChVTShVThM MBLY 'yVBUr NTShDV 'yUrYHM MBLY- 'aYSh M'aYN YVShB.
'aMUrThY 'aK-ThYUr'aY 'aVThY ThQChY MVSUr VL'a-YKUrTh M'yVNH KL 'aShUr-PhQDThY 'yLYH 'aKN HShKYMV HShChYThV KL 'yLYLVThM.
LKN ChKV-LY N'aM-YHVH LYVM QVMY L'yD KY MShPhTY L'aSPh GVYM LQBTShY MMLKVTh LShPhK 'yLYHM Z'yMY KL ChUrVN 'aPhY KY B'aSh QN'aThY Th'aKL KL-H'aUrTSh.
KY-'aZ 'aHPhK 'aL-'yMYM ShPhH BUrVUrH LQUr'a KLM BShM YHVH L'yBDV ShKM 'aChD.
M'yBUr LNHUrY-KVSh 'yThUrY BTh-PhVTShY YVBLVN MNChThY.
BYVM HHV'a L'a ThBVShY MKL 'yLYLThYK 'aShUr PhSh'yTh BY KY-'aZ 'aSYUr MQUrBK 'yLYZY G'aVThK VL'a-ThVSPhY LGBHH 'yVD BHUr QDShY.
VHSh'aUrThY BQUrBK 'yM 'yNY VDL VChSV BShM YHVH.
Sh'aUrYTh YShUr'aL L'a-Y'yShV 'yVLH VL'a-YDBUrV KZB VL'a-YMTSh'a BPhYHM LShVN ThUrMYTh KY-HMH YUr'yV VUrBTShV V'aYN MChUrYD.
UrNY BTh-TShYVN HUrY'yV YShUr'aL ShMChY V'yLZY BKL-LB BTh YUrVShLM.
HSYUr YHVH MShPhTYK PhNH 'aYBK MLK YShUr'aL YHVH BQUrBK L'a-ThYUr'aY Ur'y 'yVD.
BYVM HHV'a Y'aMUr LYUrVShLM 'aL-ThYUr'aY TShYVN 'aL-YUrPhV YDYK.
YHVH 'aLHYK BQUrBK GBVUr YVShY'y YShYSh 'yLYK BShMChH YChUrYSh B'aHBThV YGYL 'yLYK BUrNH.
NVGY MMV'yD 'aSPhThY MMK HYV MSh'aTh 'yLYH ChUrPhH.
HNNY 'yShH 'aTh-KL-M'yNYK B'yTh HHY'a VHVSh'yThY 'aTh-HTShL'yH VHNDChH 'aQBTSh VShMThYM LThHLH VLShM BKL-H'aUrTSh BShThM.
B'yTh HHY'a 'aBY'a 'aThKM VB'yTh QBTShY 'aThKM KY-'aThN 'aThKM LShM VLThHLH BKL 'yMY H'aUrTSh BShVBY 'aTh-ShBVThYKM L'yYNYKM 'aMUr YHVH.
